.SH NAME
ichabod \- automate tests against a website using multiple headless browsers.  
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ichabod
.RI "file"
.SH DESCRIPTION
Ichabod allows you to create multiple headless webkit browsers for automated testing
.B ichabod
commands.
.PP
